Introduction

TOUCH (short for The Original Undeniable Charismatic Homme) was a five-member boy group formed by YYJ Entertainment. Originally a 7-member group, they made their debut on October 22, 2010 with the self-titled EP 'Touch'.

Throughout the groups active years, they faced multiple lineup changes. The original lineup consisted of members Sungyong, Hanjun, Younghun, Minseok, Junyong, Sunwoong, and Dabin. After the departures of Hanjun, Minseok, and Dabin in 2011, members Jaewook and Chulmin were added. Shortly after, in 2012, members Younghun and Junyong left, and new member Kanghyun was added. However, Kanghyun left in 2013 and was replaced by Sangwook.

The group eventually disbanded in early 2016.
